Ghosting is a pertinent issue in modern dating relationships. This Valentine's @mtvindia, connects with the youth to let them know that there is always a chance to solve things through communication before looking at Ghosting as the default action, afterall who knows you may be giving up on something fun just because you didn't ask. 

Isliye Iss Valentine's Singles Ke Hit Mein Jaari, ki 'Ghost Nahi, Pehle Clear Karo'.

#Collab #MTVIndia #ValentinesDay #ValentinesWeek

Amaltas is turning heads this Valentine’s Day with a bold guerrilla marketing campaign across Delhi NCR! 

Giant red gift boxes, elegantly wrapped and floating with helium balloons, are popping up at hotspots like Connaught Place, Khan Market, Galleria Market and India Gate.

But there’s more than meets the eye—each box comes with a QR code, leading passersby to explore Amaltas’ exquisite collection of sustainable, lab-grown diamond jewelry. 

A campaign as brilliant as the diamonds themselves!

#AmaltasValentine #labdiamonds #Collab #Amaltas #ValentinesDay @amaltas.jewels

CRAZE by Swiss Beauty just dropped an AI-generated rap anthem, and it’s straight fire! 
Blending music, beauty, and tech, this track is all about unapologetic self-expression and main-character energy. From The Trendsetter to The Dreamer, The Rebel to The Girl Next Door- there is something for everyone. 

With a groovy beat and a vibe that’s anything but basic, this anthem isn’t here to follow trends—it’s here to create them.
